headline: PayPal Brings Its Stablecoin to Stellar for Cross-Border Remittances, Payments Financing
summary: PayPal USD (PYUSD) plans to use Stellar for new payments and remittance use cases, as well as bringing PayFi options to millions of users and merchants.

headline: PayPal USD (PYUSD) Plans to Use Stellar for New Use Cases
summary: PayPal today announced plans to make the PayPal USD (PYUSD) stablecoin available on the Stellar network pending regulatory approval by the New York State Department of Financial Services (NYDFS)1. Stellar is a blockchain designed for fast, low-cost payments and real-world utility.
